{"tid":2331561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法武肺死亡率17% 高流感近三倍","createTime":"2020-12-19T01:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T02:06:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a65eaabfd2fb8cdbc94a526306fb8e24a712afef","tid":2331561,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:46:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/UEXHELZXH5HZVNASORPXSF5Y4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FUEXHELZXH5HZVNASORPXSF5Y4E%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=f6315809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FUEXHELZXH5HZVNASORPXSF5Y4E%2F&h=d538d96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/UEXHELZXH5HZVNASORPXSF5Y4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n法武肺死亡率17% 高流感近三倍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eMt3y2AuZ97Ui4JSlWC_f3DMjiY=/1297x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7OCX4N6ABRBQXMME3HMMGLLC7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeMt3y2AuZ97Ui4JSlWC_f3DMjiY%3D%2F1297x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7OCX4N6ABRBQXMME3HMMGLLC7M.jpg&h=a0ed8897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■印度有人製作武肺病毒蛋糕諷刺致命病毒。<br />\n<br />\n質疑武漢肺炎抗疫措施的人，常指一年死於季節性流感的人更多，不值得為武肺限制活動封城。但法國一項研究顯示，武肺死亡率差不多是流感的三倍。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美批出莫德納全球第一針  九成人接種後疼痛 專家關注副作用<br />\n這項由法國國家健康與醫學研究院和第戎大學領導的研究，比較當地今年3至4月武肺首波疫情逾8.9萬入院武肺病人，以及前年12月至去年2月逾4.5萬入院流感病人的數據，指前者有16.9%人死亡，後者則是。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n研究員指2018至19年流感季節已是法國近五年最致命，相比武肺還是差了一大截，並指流感入院數字少武肺約一半，或因民眾之前感染過流感和接種過疫苗，有一定免疫力。但該研究顯示18歲以下兒童染武肺入院率。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：彭斯直播接種增公眾信心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母染疫嬰兒有抗體<br />\n<br />\n另外，新加坡一項對當地16名感染武肺孕婦的小型研究顯示，孕婦染疫後病情相對於一般人。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社"},{"pid":"7ce264454ef564309d61d87677e097f0437a8a89","tid":2331561,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"咁至係架嘛<br />\n0.x無人驚"},{"pid":"bb54a5a4bc70dd7f3cd4bf3c7e315481fcf03060","tid":2331561,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"好多無症狀感染者，其實感染人數係低估，死亡率就變相高咗"},{"pid":"e9d85f5e3ed605571f8d6771dd8d881f7270ef34","tid":2331561,"uid":28547,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb54a5a4bc70dd7f3cd4bf3c7e315481fcf03060","tid":2331561,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"好多無症狀感染者，其實感染人數係低估，死亡率就變相高咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"你講流感？"},{"pid":"47756e23b7ec0f2a93df76fd93e8affd50e52236","tid":2331561,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d85f5e3ed605571f8d6771dd8d881f7270ef34","tid":2331561,"uid":28547,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb54a5a4bc70dd7f3cd4bf3c7e315481fcf03060","tid":2331561,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"好多無症狀感染者，其實感染人數係低估，死亡率就變相高咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"你講流感？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbe31755125ff7701d1e406ba2ca806ed110c7b","tid":2331561,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"尋日先話瑞典放任唔理死亡率先2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇差咁遠"},{"pid":"7d7c29680564247382cd3b94bef8e7b57d5a0599","tid":2331561,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />jUsT a fLu~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />losor 甘都驚<img src=\"/assets/fac